info.title: RamQuest Actions
info.description:
This connector streamlines your RamQuest title production software solution processes, whether CCE or Horizon, by offering a suite of actions which can be performed from order retrieval and creation to document and task management. 
Note: This connector is currently in Preview/Beta status. RamQuest customers interested in becoming early adopters should contact their RamQuest representative. If selected, RamQuest will provide the necessary credentials to access the connector.

parameters.name: orderId
parameters.description: Specify the File # to be retrieved

put.description: Add a note to an existing RamQuest order

parameters.name: orderId
parameters.description: Specify the File # to which to add the note

post.description: Add a document to an existing RamQuest order

parameters.name: orderId
parameters.description: Specify the File # to which to add the document

parameters.name: fileName
parameters.description: Specify a name for the document including its file extension e.g. document_name.pdf

parameters.name: documentCategory
parameters.description: Specify a category to assign to the document. If not provided, the category will be unassigned

parameters.name: fileContent
parameters.description: Document content from cloud storage connector (Microsoft OneDrive, Dropbox, etc.)

get.description: Retrieve an existing document on an existing RamQuest order

parameters.name: orderId
parameters.description: Specify the File # to retrieve document from

publisher.description: The publishing author of the document

documentBase64.description: Gets or Sets Document in Base64 encoding

get.description: Retrieve existing task(s) on an existing RamQuest order

parameters.name: orderId
parameters.description: Specify the File # for which to retrieve the tasks

parameters.name: taskId
parameters.description: Leave empty to retrieve all tasks for an order or specify a task that exists on the order

post.description: Add a task to an existing RamQuest order

parameters.name: orderId
parameters.description: Specify the File # to which to add the task

put.description: Update an existing task on an existing RamQuest order

parameters.name: orderId
parameters.description: Specify the File # to which to update the task

404.description: Not Found, OrderId or TaskId does not exist

post.description: Create a new identity search order with an integration service provider and return the result as a JSON object. This action is allowed to run 5 seconds before failing. As a rule, we recommend not including more than 10 individuals and businesses in your search to reduce the risk of timeout errors. Note that a single party with both an individual full name and a business name counts as 2 inputs to the search. Also, consider setting a retry policy on this action from the settings tab so that failed runs will be tried again.

parameters.name: sm-source-file-id
parameters.description: File number to which parties are associated.

parameters.name: pdf
parameters.description: Indicates to generate PDF in response.

parameters.name: body
parameters.description: Parties to search against based on business and/or individual full names

post.description: Create a new identity search order with an integration service provider and return the result as a PDF in binary format. This action is allowed to run 5 seconds before failing. As a rule, we recommend not including more than 10 individuals and businesses in your search to reduce the risk of timeout errors. Note that a single party with both an individual full name and a business name counts as 2 inputs to the search. Also, consider setting a retry policy on this action from the settings tab so that failed runs will be tried again.

parameters.name: sm-source-file-id
parameters.description: File number to which parties are associated.

parameters.name: pdf
parameters.description: Indicates to generate PDF in response.

parameters.name: body
parameters.description: Parties to search against based on business and/or individual full names
